long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to OrthoVoIP!!! We are a team of experts who are passionate about helping orthodontic practices improve their communication processes and enhance patient satisfaction. Our VoIP phone system was created with the needs of orthodontic practices in mind, and we are proud to offer a solution that is flexible, customizable, and designed to meet the unique needs of each office.

Our system was created by a doctor who has firsthand experience running both private practices and DSOs. He understands the challenges and unique needs of each type of practice, and this knowledge has been incorporated into the design of our system. As a result, our VoIP phone system is specifically tailored to meet the needs of orthodontic practices, providing a communication solution that is effective, efficient, and reliable.

This extension works in sync with the OrthoVoip product and is designed to alert the user when a call lands and also provide the details of the caller.
